{"tid":1839884,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"既然想封關，點解各邊境口岸嘅人員唔一齊罷？","createTime":"2020-01-24T15:34:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T16:18:09.000Z","uid":180442,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"349355e8ab4d9706c394852dbee2c06ff6144a0b","tid":1839884,"uid":180442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T15:34:07.000Z","msg":"各<span style=\"color: red;\">邊境口岸</span>係隔絕鄰國人嘅第一道防線。<br />\n<br />\n我知你哋個個都人心惶惶。防護措施不足，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">到呢一刻都淨係得個口罩。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n既然醫護發起罷工，各口岸嘅工作人員都一齊罷啦！<br />\n<br />\n「突發」四個醫療工會不排除於初四後發起工業行動！(終極整合）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837445\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837445</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">建議同醫護一齊搞</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光 復 香 港</span></span>"},{"pid":"b89fdb9d33634c8e7186b59cdc58ce6940484dbf","tid":1839884,"uid":180442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T15:34:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"62d8bd37e266881908d06a3bf241eb854619000e","tid":1839884,"uid":51068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T15:39:00.000Z","msg":"全靠抗爭者，中國人先減少來港，肺炎傳染程度先減少<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1833923\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1833923</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1573c52d249a4e28518bff0a94d88a0d6dcd02ac","tid":1839884,"uid":51068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T15:39:11.000Z","msg":"[內幕分析] 林奠用萬條人命落賭注，如果醫護市民唔團結，林奠就可以用病毒翻盤<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1839427\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1839427</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"66e33c0726d17ede8907d2423c03aecc96a27d41","tid":1839884,"uid":175346,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T15:42:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1a90b68a94caf6184cf5f11bfd54